comments: Curry (BKN) makes contact with Harden's (PHI) elbow, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Following the pass, Melton (PHI) establishes himself in O'Neale's (BKN) path and he does not deliver illegal contact.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in Melton's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Embiid (PHI) and Curry (BKN) briefly engage off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Embiid positions himself to receive the post entry pass.
Claxton (BKN) and Embiid (PHI) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Claxton (BKN) initiates contact to Embiid's (PHI) front that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Irving (BKN) brings his off-arm toward Melton (PHI) and marginal contact occurs as Irving releases away without applying any force during the driving shot attempt
Embiid (PHI) jumps to contest the oncoming driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Irving's (BKN) lower body.
Maxey (PHI) establishes himself in O'Neale's (BKN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.

Claxton (BKN) brings his arm forward to contest the driving shot attempt, and marginal contact occurs with Harden's (PHI) head. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Harris (PHI) is moving alongside Irving's (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Embiid (PHI) is the last to touch the ball before it goes OOB.
O'Neale (BKN) inbounds the ball in under 5 seconds.
Embiid (PHI) grabs and pulls Watanabe's (BKN) jersey away from his body off-ball, affecting Watanabe's FOM as he pursues the inbound pass.
Embiid (PHI) brings his hand toward Watanabe (BKN) and marginal contact occurs with Watanabe's body during the driving shot attempt.
Harris (BKN) inbounds the ball in under 5 seconds.
Curry (BKN) commits a take foul on Melton (PHI).
O'Neale (BKN) inbounds the ball in under 5 seconds.
